{"tid":1915542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"積極支持反送中 　「好鄰舍北區教會」崇拜疑被警監視　轟打壓宗教自由","createTime":"2020-03-08T09:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T09:47:46.000Z","uid":53379,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bf4f793df7ef7b8ce12c4cb261bf8c7485d71434","tid":1915542,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">積極支持反送中 　「好鄰舍北區教會」崇拜疑被警監視　轟打壓宗教自由</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Untitled-1-20_jlpMW_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FUntitled-1-20_jlpMW_1200x0.png&h=5a649bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在過去大半年來積極支持反送中運動的「好鄰舍北區教會」，懷疑教會近日遭警方監察。教會稱在上周日（1日）崇拜活動期間，有軍裝警員到場了解是否有「公眾活動」，而昨日（7日）崇拜期間再有多部警車及疑似便衣警在附近觀察。教會質疑當局是以白色恐怖打壓宗教自由。<br />\n<br />\n「好鄰舍北區教會」在FB發文，指下午2至6時有四輛警車經過教會門口，其中三輛更是在短短一小時崇拜期間經過。有教友戶外崇拜時發現，最少兩名疑似便衣在附近觀察，行蹤鬼祟。教會質疑便衣警是在崇拜時進行監察。<br />\n<br />\n「好鄰舍北區教會」亦透露，上周日約中午12時，有三位軍裝警員曾到場，了解教會是否有「公眾活動」需要協助，警員在約一分鐘後離開。警方行動令崇拜稍暫中斷，「難怪有智慧的教友說，『了解』是虛的，背後要表達的，正是『司馬昭之心，路人皆見』。」<br />\n<br />\n位於粉嶺的「好鄰舍北區教會」 ，近月來都積極支持反送中運動。陳凱興傳道是「守護孩子行動」的發起人之一，曾在金鐘發起絕食行動。他曾經在元旦遊行當晚被捕。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》正就事件向警方查詢，目前暫待回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E5%A5%BD%E9%84%B0%E8%88%8D%E5%8C%97%E5%8D%80%E6%95%99%E6%9C%83-%E5%B4%87%E6%8B%9C%E7%96%91%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96-%E8%BD%9F%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1/?fbclid=IwAR2LDy0m4ENeTL3ryQm9rsXNGGKsmrxl9uD3qsiJSKo9St0MhJXf1a3FKMQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A9%258D%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E9%2584%25B0%25E8%2588%258D%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%25B4%2587%25E6%258B%259C%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25A6%2596-%25E8%25BD%259F%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2LDy0m4ENeTL3ryQm9rsXNGGKsmrxl9uD3qsiJSKo9St0MhJXf1a3FKMQ&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5BwzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=e378a816\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A9%258D%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E9%2584%25B0%25E8%2588%258D%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%25B4%2587%25E6%258B%259C%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25A6%2596-%25E8%25BD%259F%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2LDy0m4ENeTL3ryQm9rsXNGGKsmrxl9uD3qsiJSKo9St0MhJXf1a3FKMQ&h=d78b5c59\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E5%A5%BD%E9%84%B0%E8%88%8D%E5%8C%97%E5%8D%80%E6%95%99%E6%9C%83-%E5%B4%87%E6%8B%9C%E7%96%91%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96-%E8%BD%9F%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1/?fbclid=IwAR2LDy0m4ENeTL3ryQm9rsXNGGKsmrxl9uD3qsiJSKo9St0MhJXf1a3FKMQ</a>"},{"pid":"3a5890ac1837c23a4a5fe9e652c2fb36c2d9ea0e","tid":1915542,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:34:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"46947af910992c8f611144dfe3f29a3a4e29f79f","tid":1915542,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed8f5f6857354ab9919e4647b765b8ac722554f","tid":1915542,"uid":288913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:36:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"be430d6a2c3f0f437b18e0f62ab89ed7234cd3a7","tid":1915542,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB